Thanks again for inviting me to this group - what an awesome group of
people!! Two things:

1) As mentioned in my last call we're making our platform available to
select clients. After I spoke to my business partner we've agreed to make
it available to anyone in this network - it just seems like everyone you've
brought into it are looking to create a net positive global impact. Those
are the kinds of people we want to work with.

